WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.720 --> 00:00:05.800
Xiaoyu, you are finally willing to find me

2
00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:07.760
I called you several times and you didn't answer

3
00:00:07.760 --> 00:00:09.420
I don't know how anxious I am

4
00:00:10.360 --> 00:00:11.700
Give me back my necklace

5
00:00:12.640 --> 00:00:13.620
What necklace?

6
00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:16.400
Stop pretending, I've checked the hospital's surveillance

7
00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:17.800
You just took it away.

8
00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:19.440
This necklace is worthless

9
00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:21.000
You went to great lengths to steal him

10
00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:21.860
Then why?

11
00:00:23.280 --> 00:00:24.560
Xiaoyu, what are you talking about?

12
00:00:24.560 --> 00:00:25.620
I don't understand.

13
00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:27.880
Tell me which necklace you like.

14
00:00:27.880 --> 00:00:28.720
I'll buy it for you right away

15
00:00:28.720 --> 00:00:31.120
Right? I mean it to you

16
00:00:31.120 --> 00:00:33.460
How could I possibly take your stuff?

17
00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:34.760
tell the truth

18
00:00:35.280 --> 00:00:36.420
Then I'll tell you now.

19
00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:42.100
Xiaoyu, we are getting married, what are you playing with me?

20
00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:46.840
You can't treat me like this because of my love and tolerance for you.

21
00:00:46.840 --> 00:00:48.360
Then I will be sad too.

22
00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:49.820
When do I scold molecules?

23
00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:53.060
I told you we broke up

24
00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:56.220
Xiaoyu, I have already gone to the Qin family to propose marriage

25
00:00:56.400 --> 00:00:58.680
Mrs. Du and Mr. Qin have agreed

26
00:00:58.680 --> 00:01:02.500
After a while, pick a good day and prepare the wedding for us.

27
00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:05.660
What they didn't go through my Prodos will decide

